text: Thomas Batliner (born 3 April 1959) is a Liechtenstein equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Liechtenstein male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Liechtenstein Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Chur
